# Google OAuth 2.0 credentials from Google Cloud Console.
# See README.md → "Google OAuth Setup" for step-by-step instructions.
#
# IMPORTANT: Create a "Web application" OAuth client (not "Chrome extension").
# The extension uses chrome.identity.launchWebAuthFlow + PKCE, which requires
# the Web application type with an Authorized redirect URI:
#   https://<your-extension-id>.chromiumapp.org/
#
# The client_secret is considered public by Google for installed-app OAuth
# (it ships inside the built extension). PKCE protects the token exchange.
# Do NOT reuse your production Web app credentials here.

GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=
